    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. can u get a bit more specific with the grooming part though? like for hair and stuff. i have some clients who might have different hair textures or styles, and i want to make sure they know what to do so they don't seem \"unprofessional\" or anything. like what's the standard?",
